2000-02-18  Samuel Tardieu  <sam@inf.enst.fr>

	* sockets-thin.ads: Use System.Address instead of Iovec_Access, to
	simplify the interface.

2000-01-25  Samuel Tardieu  <sam@inf.enst.fr>

	* sockets-thin.ads: Change caddr_t by System.Address as it is more
	consistent to do so.

2000-01-07  Samuel Tardieu  <sam@inf.enst.fr>

	* sockets-naming.adb: Protect non-reentrant calls with a
	mutex.

1999-06-16  Samuel Tardieu  <sam@inf.enst.fr>

	* Makefile.am (install-data-local): Use $(mkinstalldirs) instead
	of mkdir to create directories.

	* sockets.ads: Add a new field that records whether Shutdown has
	been called in both directions or not.

	* sockets.adb: If Shutdown has been closed in both direction,
	close the socket so that we do not experience a memory leak.

1998-04-06  Samuel Tardieu  <sam@inf.enst.fr>

	* constants.c: Use new config.h to include the right files

	* constants.sh: Use a new scheme to compute constants

	* Makefile.am: Use new constants.sh

1998-03-22  Samuel Tardieu  <sam@inf.enst.fr>

	* sockets-utils.adb: Add an explicit raise Program_Error to work
	around a GNAT limitation that does not recognize Raise_Exception
	as raising an exception.
